title: Kiss Person Man Dark Skin Tone Medium Light Skin Tone
description: Illustrates a loving kiss between two men, featuring one with a dark skin tone and the other with a medium-light skin tone. It's used to express romantic connection and affection between men.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, the kiss emoji between a man with a dark skin tone and a person with a medium-light skin tone is rendered with tender intimacy and warmth. Apple's signature realistic lighting and smooth gradients highlight the gentle curve of their faces as they lean in for a kiss, with soft rounded edges emphasizing their closeness. This emoji beautifully symbolizes romantic affection, passion, and deep personal connection between two individuals.
